                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#022E01] to-[#4ade80] rounded-full"></span>
                                Growth strategy planning
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#022E01] to-[#4ade80] rounded-full"></span>
                                Investment preparation
