                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Flexible Engagement</h3>
                            <p class="text-white/80">Project-based, retainer, or milestone-based consulting arrangements</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300">
